# TIPTAP VPS MCP mapping

This workspace folder is **TAPTAP_sauth** (TIPTAP South Africa). Use only the VPS MCP server dedicated to this project.

## This project uses

| MCP server name (exact) | Use for |
|-------------------------|---------|
| **TIPTAP SOUTH AFRICA** | Production/staging host for this Laravel app — deploy, Docker, nginx, `.env`, logs, `php artisan`, queue workers, database on SA VPS |

When the user asks to SSH, deploy, fix production, rebuild Docker, or run server commands for **South Africa / sauth**, call MCP tools on **`TIPTAP SOUTH AFRICA`** only.

## Do not use for TAPTAP_sauth (unless user explicitly names another project)

| MCP server | Belongs to |
|------------|------------|
| **TITAP BOT SERVE** | `TAPTAP tz` — WhatsApp bot (`tiptopbot`) for Tanzania |
| **TIPTAP Saloon** | `Saloon ver` — Saloon Laravel app |

Never deploy SA code to TZ bot or Saloon VPS by default.

## How to invoke

Use `CallMcpTool` with `server` set to the exact MCP name (e.g. `"TIPTAP SOUTH AFRICA"`). Read the tool schema under the MCP descriptors before calling.

## Region note

- Country/market: South Africa (ZA flag on landing/login where applicable)
- Do not confuse with **TAPTAP TZ** (Tanzania) or **Saloon ver**
